<!-- Bag Mat v3: transparent boxes (frame-only rstyle) + bright colored labels. -->
<!-- 3 big zones on top, 3 smaller zones below. Boxes are click-through. -->
<!-- See-through by design; grab the title bar to move, X to close. -->
